    "body": "## Summary\n\nWipes `core/cli/` source and rebuilds it as a minimal, buildable CLI shell per the plan at `thoughts/shared/plans/2026-04-24-core-cli-barebones-reset.md`. The existing `login`/`logout`/`listen` trio hard-coded `/api/cli/*` and `/api/gateway/stream` server contracts that may not survive the platform consolidation, and `src/index.ts` was already `export {}` — so this clears the slate rather than carrying dead assumptions into the rewrite.\n\n- Deletes `src/commands/*`, `src/lib/*`, `src/env.ts`, old `src/index.ts`; rewrites `src/bin.ts` as a bare commander program (`--help`, `--version` only).\n- Drops runtime deps `@inquirer/select`, `@t3-oss/env-core`, `eventsource-parser`, `open`, `ora`, `picocolors`, `zod` and the unused `main`/`types`/`exports` fields.\n- Collapses `tsup.config.ts` to a single-entry build (no dual-entry, no dts, target `node22`); drops the now-unused `LIGHTFAST_API_URL`/`LIGHTFAST_API_KEY` entries from `core/cli/turbo.json`.\n- Leaves changeset plumbing intact (`.changeset/pre.json`, `ci-core.yml`, `verify-changeset.yml`) so the next alpha can cut cleanly. Version stays at `0.1.0`.\n\nNet diff: 14 files changed, +14 / -855. Build output: single `dist/bin.mjs` at 223 bytes.\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [x] `pnpm install` succeeds\n- [x] `pnpm --filter @lightfastai/cli typecheck` exits 0\n- [x] `pnpm --filter @lightfastai/cli build` produces only `dist/bin.mjs` (with `#!/usr/bin/env node` shebang)\n- [x] `pnpm turbo typecheck --filter=@lightfastai/cli --filter=@lightfastai/mcp --filter=lightfast` passes (matches `ci-core.yml`)\n- [x] `pnpm turbo build --filter=@lightfastai/cli --filter=@lightfastai/mcp --filter=lightfast` passes (matches `ci-core.yml`)\n- [x] Root `pnpm check` (Biome) passes\n- [x] `pnpm turbo typecheck` across the whole repo: 54/54 tasks successful\n- [x] `node core/cli/dist/bin.mjs --help` prints the expected usage block\n- [x] `node core/cli/dist/bin.mjs --version` prints `0.1.0`",
